## WORKFLOW

- GATE: ASK & STOP if project params (env, region, Jira) missing.
- GIT: !Auto-test, !Auto-commit, !Auto-push. Wait for explicit prompt.
- ACP: `git add -A` -> conv commit -> push (only if requested).
- SAFETY: Ask before destructive cmds (rm, drop).
